1
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:11,800
Sorry,

2
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:12,440
I'm late.

3
00:00:12,440 --> 00:00:12,760
Meijuan,

4
00:00:12,760 --> 00:00:14,160
did you just get off work?

5
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:16,520
Thank you.

6
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:21,800
Meijuan,

7
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:23,960
I have good news to share with you.

8
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:24,560
What is it?

9
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,920
Our event this time

10
00:00:25,920 --> 00:00:27,720
has received sponsorships from various parties.

11
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:29,080
The funding problem is solved.

12
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:29,800
Really? Congratulations!

13
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:30,280
Really.

14
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,880
I'm so happy.

15
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:34,140
Let's open a bottle of wine to celebrate.

16
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:36,200
I'm not very good at drinking.

17
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:37,530
Actually, neither am I.

18
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:38,940
I easily get drunk.

19
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:40,880
Let's just have a little.

20
00:00:43,760 --> 00:00:44,240
Okay.

21
00:00:45,720 --> 00:00:46,600
Waiter!

22
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:00,920
In the past,

23
00:01:01,120 --> 00:01:04,920
I had to work 12 hours a day at a loom.

24
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:06,920
In less than a month,

25
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:09,520
my hands were completely covered in calluses.

26
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:11,820
The clothes I made myself,

27
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:14,220
I couldn't afford a single piece.

28
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,960
They would be shipped to

29
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:16,920
Shanghai,

30
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:18,400
Beijing,

31
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,960
even Hong Kong,

32
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:20,960
and the US.

33
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,440
I always wondered

34
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,160
when

35
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:26,760
I would have the opportunity

36
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,039
to visit those places.

37
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,250
I got into a university,

38
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,400
but my mom wouldn't let me go.

39
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:34,120
She wanted me to marry an

40
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:36,520
old man I had only met once.

41
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:40,680
Because I have a brother who is 6 years younger than me.

42
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:45,060
She wanted to use my bride price to pay for his college tuition.

43
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,080
Is my story very boring?

44
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,440
How could it be?

45
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:56,240
I didn't expect

46
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:58,440
your past experiences to be so pitiful.

47
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,340
It breaks my heart.

48
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,660
You are still so young,

49
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,440
right?

50
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,729
There is still a long road ahead

51
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:10,770
with infinite possibilities.

52
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:13,920
Gold will always shine.

53
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:23,160
Our company has businesses all over the country.

54
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:25,160
As long as you are willing,

55
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,680
I can take you anywhere.

56
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,160
Are you...

57
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,280
I just want you to

58
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:36,560
have more opportunities to get to know me.

59
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,440
Likewise,

60
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,570
I want to get to know you too.

61
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,480
Meijuan.

62
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:47,500
Are you single?

63
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:18,050
Then can I formally pursue you?

64
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,040
Yes.

65
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,840
Aren't you transferring to a civilian post?

66
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,170
What are you doing here?

67
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,560
So what if I am?

68
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,060
I'm here waiting for a bus.

69
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,780
Captain Li said you're going to Dongwan.

70
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:29,080
Is it any of your business where I go?

71
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,440
Aren't you off this case?

72
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,600
Attention, passengers.

73
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:34,200
Ticket checking for Dongwan has started.

74
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,480
I have to get on board.

75
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,680
Please take your luggage and belongings.

76
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,640
Go back, go back.

77
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,900
Get on the bus orderly.

78
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,440
Thank you for your cooperation.

79
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:44,159
Attention, passengers.

80
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:47,600
The bus to Dongwan is now boarding. Let's go back.

81
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,060
Please take your luggage.

82
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,000
Eat well.

83
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,600
Liu.

84
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,200
We have someone here canceling his wife's household registration.

85
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:28,720
And I found out that a driver's license was just issued under her name.

86
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,920
Can you check if her ID card was stolen?

87
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,720
Sure.

88
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,600
Liu Meijuan, right?

89
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:33,960
Yes.

90
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:34,760
Just a moment.

91
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,440
I found it.

92
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,960
This is a copy of her driver's license.

93
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:43,480
Take a look.

94
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,280
Let me see.

95
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,770
By the way, Meijuan.

96
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:53,300
We've been dating for so long.

97
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:54,820
Don't you think

98
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,890
it's time to let our families know?

99
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,780
When you have time,

100
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:04,490
I'll take you to meet my dad.

101
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,760
I'll prepare the gifts.

102
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,360
He will definitely like you.

103
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,040
There's no rush for this.

104
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,020
Let's talk about it later.

105
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,840
Whatever you say.

106
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,560
Then see you tomorrow.

107
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,560
See you tomorrow.

108
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,600
Who are you?

109
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,490
How long have you known her?

110
00:07:50,159 --> 00:07:51,360
You mean Meijuan?

111
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,690
You must be her brother.

112
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:54,680
Hello.

113
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,760
I'm Li Xuebo,

114
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,300
Meijuan's boyfriend.

115
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,540
We've been dating for a while.

116
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,400
Dating?

117
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:11,360
You don't know her very well yet, do you?

118
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:17,400
I don't really want you to have any more contact.

119
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,760
This is between the two of us.

120
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,560
You don't need to worry about it.

121
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,560
Then you can try.

122
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,400
If I find out you're still in contact,

123
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:33,600
it won't be as simple as just a chat next time.

124
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,680
Where were you so late?

125
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:39,760
Working overtime.

126
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,400
Cao Aiyuan,

127
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,760
get back here!

128
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,820
Are you crazy drunk again?

129
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,500
Working overtime?

130
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:59,400
Then who was the guy that just brought you back?

131
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,960
A client from our hotel.

132
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:09,840
He praised me to the manager before,

133
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,840
so the manager promoted me,

134
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,960
and even gave me a raise.

135
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:18,060
The manager told me to treat him well,

136
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:19,960
so I took him out for dinner today

137
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,960
to express my gratitude.

138
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,260
Is there a problem?

139
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,700
Is that how people show gratitude nowadays?

140
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:29,890
Then what's the difference between you and a hooker?

141
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,120
Can you show me some respect?

142
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,080
Cao Aiyuan,

143
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:37,130
I respect you very much.

144
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,760
You didn't come back all night that day.

145
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:40,280
Where did you go?

146
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:41,320
With who?

147
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,250
With him, right?

148
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,610
You slept with him, didn't you?

149
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,400
Tell me!

150
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,400
If you must ask,

151
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:56,370
we both drank too much that day.

152
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,250
It was just an accident.

153
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:02,560
An accident?

154
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:06,520
Cao Aiyuan, how have I treated you?

155
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:10,120
I wake up early and stay up late, weathering storms for you.

156
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,980
I only make a few dozen bucks a day.

157
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:15,200
When people pointed at my face and cursed me in the market,

158
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,240
did I say a word?

159
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,800
I was just like a dog!

160
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:22,360
You know what kind of person I, Hua Weihong, used to be.

161
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:26,880
Now you just lightly brush it off as an accident,

162
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:27,880
that you drank too much.

163
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,880
Are you doing right by me?

164
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:36,600
Are you doing right by me?

165
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:40,520
Didn't you send me to sleep with others before?

166
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:41,480
That's different.

167
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,000
How is it different?

168
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,480
We are living a settled life now.

169
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:48,640
Tell me how we can live our lives from now on?

170
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:49,880
How can we live?

171
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:55,200
I'm pregnant.

172
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,240
What?

173
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:00,720
Whose is it?

174
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:04,920
Mine.

175
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:08,040
I'm asking, whose is it?

176
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:10,720
Whose?

177
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,160
Mine.

178
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,200
You know what I mean.

179
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:18,240
I'm asking whose baby it is.

180
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,560
Is it mine or his?

181
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:27,650
It has nothing to do with either of you.

182
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:28,840
What are you...

183
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,720
It's my own baby.

184
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,760
I will take responsibility for it myself.

185
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:31,290
Will you?

186
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,920
What are you talking about?

187
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:35,320
What do you mean it has nothing to do with me?

188
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:38,760
It's fine.

189
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:41,120
Let's not care whose baby it is right now.

190
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:45,130
I just want to ask you one thing.

191
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,360
If you have to choose now,

192
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:49,240
do you choose me or him?

193
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,720
Answer me.

194
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,200
Aiyuan.

195
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,260
I'm sorry, Aiyuan.

196
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,080
I'm sorry.

197
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,240
I was wrong just now.

198
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,160
It was my fault.

199
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,960
No matter whose baby this is,

200
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:09,720
it's our baby.

201
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,520
I promise you.

202
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,960
I'll work harder from now on,

203
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,120
make good money,

204
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:17,040
and take good care of you and the child.

205
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:17,500
Aiyuan.

206
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:18,660
Aiyuan.

207
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:20,480
Is that okay?

208
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:27,720
Let me think about it.

209
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:55,600
That's a lot of stuff today.

210
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:03,960
You stinking sugarcane seller!

211
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,290
Do you have a death wish?

212
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:12,620
What are you doing?

213
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,320
Fei.

214
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:17,360
Here for fruit again?

215
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:21,160
You can have some,

216
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,260
but help me get something.

217
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:27,720
Try this.

218
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:30,400
It's a local specialty of Dongwan.

219
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:32,360
See if you like it.

220
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:35,720
It's been so long,

221
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:38,760
and I still don't know where your hometown is.

222
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:39,560
Guangnan.

223
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,520
Guangnan.

224
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:51,330
But I saw your registered residence is local.

225
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:54,250
Did you investigate me?

226
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:59,170
I'm sorry, Meijuan.

227
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,760
I know

228
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:03,290
it's a bit offensive to you.

229
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:06,720
But I want to know everything about you.

230
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,360
If you have any difficulties,

231
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,760
you can tell me directly.

232
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:13,440
I can help you.

233
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:16,200
I don't want us to have

234
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:18,240
any secrets from each other.

235
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,920
If I were a fugitive criminal,

236
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,130
would you report me?

237
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:27,240
No.

238
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,970
Do you think I'm not a criminal,

239
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:34,490
or would you just not report me?

240
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:39,320
You definitely wouldn't be a criminal.

241
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:49,920
Meijuan.

242
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,520
I know I said too much

243
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:54,450
and did too much.

244
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,120
I made you unhappy.

245
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,180
I admit my mistake.

246
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,240
Let's drop it.

247
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:02,120
Let's eat first.

248
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:02,840
Okay?

249
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:03,680
Try it.

250
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:05,560
It's our specialty.

251
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:07,220
See if it suits your taste.

252
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:08,200
If you don't like it,

253
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:09,660
we'll change it tomorrow.

254
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:22,560
You eat too.

255
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:35,240
Is it good?

256
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:36,920
Yes.
